40:51.080 --> 40:52.502
(Sally grunts)

41:05.290 --> 41:06.780
- (Sally): Ray!

41:08.630 --> 41:11.691
Stop! Stop!
- Hey, hey, hey!

41:11.730 --> 41:13.129
You're one of us now, huh?

41:13.170 --> 41:16.060
Why don't you just enjoy it?

41:16.100 --> 41:18.899
Enjoy it!
And join the party! Ha ha!

41:20.770 --> 41:22.670
That's my boy!

41:24.110 --> 41:25.202
Ah!

41:25.250 --> 41:27.571
- (Sally): Aidan! Aidan!

41:27.610 --> 41:30.216
- (Aidan): Hey! What are you
